### Post Summary

<div class="blog-entry">
  <div class="summary-image" style='background-image:url("{{data.image}}")'></div>
  <h2><a href="/blog/{{filename}}">{{data.header}}</a></h2>
  <div class="byline">{{formatDateTime data.posted "MMMM Do YYYY"}}</div>
  <div class="abstract ellipsis">
